Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with high specific electrolyte surface area was fabricated using the multi-pass extrusion process.
Titulo: Fabrication of seven cells in single tubular solid oxide fuel cell using multi-pass extrusion process

Sentencas: In this design, one tube contained 7 individual fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of seven cells in single tubular solid oxide fuel cell using multi-pass extrusion process

Sentencas: The outer diameter of the tube was 5 mm and 4.1-4.2 mm after extrusion and sintering, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of seven cells in single tubular solid oxide fuel cell using multi-pass extrusion process

Sentencas: The length of the cell was optimized to 3-5 cm with continuous channels of 400-450 mu m in diameter.
Titulo: Fabrication of seven cells in single tubular solid oxide fuel cell using multi-pass extrusion process

Sentencas: The porous microstructures of the anode and the cathode and the dense microstructure of the electrolyte were observed by scanning electron microscopy.
Titulo: Fabrication of seven cells in single tubular solid oxide fuel cell using multi-pass extrusion process

Sentencas: The relative density of the electrolyte was >96% and the thickness was 15-20 mu m.
